(2 at a time) or 2 gold to Lashun Novashine. He<BR>
can be found near the cleric guild, or walking<BR>
around in the newbie area just outside the gate.<BR>
Also, killing the putrid skeletons near grimrot's<BR>
spawn will raise your faction to a point (after<BR>
that is maxed, you need to do the Lashun quest<BR>
for bone chips or gold to get it even higher)<BR>
Be warned, it takes super faction. After maxing<BR>
faction with killing putrids, i had to hand Lashun<BR>
around 1500 gold , 2 at a time to get my faction<BR>
to the point where he gave me the quest.<BR>
